---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<div class="pt-8 text-center">
  <div
    class="relative glass-card rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-16 overflow-hidden"
  >
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ea7601]/5 via-[#ea7601]/10 to-[#ea7601]/5 rounded-3xl"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10">
      <h2
        style="font-family: 'Audiowide', sans-serif;"
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-4"
      >
        Ready to Create?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 font-sans">
        Rig/2 正在重新定义 Minecraft 动画的创作标准。<br />
        加入已经在使用它的创作者行列。
      </p>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ea7601] to-[#ff9a3c] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-[#ea7601]/30 uppercase tracking-wider text-lg group"
      >
        Get Started Free
        <ArrowRight
          className="w-6 h-6 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
        />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="pt-24 pb-12 text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase"
  >
    Started at 2025-10-09 | Rig/2: Define the New Standard.
  </div>

  <div
    class="pb-8 text-gray-500 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase"
  >
    *性能表现可能因硬件配置而异，测试环境下关闭了视口布尔和视口细分。
  </div>

  <div class="pb-12 text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
    <a href="/mozi-rig/legacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Download Legacy Version</a>
  </div>
</div>
